name: testNotAvailableDeleteForDefaultViewForUser
description: Verification the possibility of Deleting View From Default View To User
descriptionHtml: Verification the possibility of Deleting View From Default View To User

testStage.description: Verification the possibility of Deleting View From Default View To User

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Input the New Item name
Select Job Type on NewJobPage
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Get Header
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
click 'My Views' link from side menu
Click to create a new View
Set a View Name
Select View Type and click 'Create'
Get Header
Click on the User drop down menu on the Header
Click on the 'Configure' link from user drop down menu on the header page
Enter view name to Default View field
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Get Breadcrumb
Get the 'Dashboard' drop-down menu
Get a page form the 'Dashboard' drop-down menu
Click on a View
Verification the 'Delete View' button invisibility on the Side menu
Get Header
Click on the User drop down menu on the Header
Click on the 'Configure' link from user drop down menu on the header page
Enter view name to Default View field
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
